{"tid":1902813,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"無聊得滯 改咗中共一首歌","createTime":"2020-02-28T14:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T15:01:34.000Z","uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6c08a2401645dc48a0ecb8da30221148200e802f","tid":1902813,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:34:50.000Z","msg":"東方紅， 光照天， 天下出左一個當勞侵。<br />\n佢為天下謀興旺， Hallelujah， 救港自由大恩人。<br />\n當勞侵，愛香港， 佢係我哋嘅領羊人。<br />\n捍衛自由護香港， Hallelujah，帶領我哋照光芒<br />\n當勞侵，似陽光，照到邊度邊度光。 邊度地方有光照， Hallelujah， 嗰邊地方得光榮。<br />\n<br />\n唔好問我邊間教會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不喜勿歡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73fca8661d01641ded410e89e28a87a3560768cf","tid":1902813,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:35:11.000Z","msg":"pish 1"},{"pid":"6e51f8f9a3a37b5bc0db9a8e349ff92da181540c","tid":1902813,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:35:32.000Z","msg":"pish 2"},{"pid":"a94bb1c3ee8f2661a44c3f7e9c51e2d2988f9ebd","tid":1902813,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:53:55.000Z","msg":"pish 3"},{"pid":"a42ce681fcdaf4214446add356f5a1593c3d007a","tid":1902813,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"pish 5"},{"pid":"a457b66f84c0f44fc7b131ec5f34c3025ebf2553","tid":1902813,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:54:39.000Z","msg":"pish 4"},{"pid":"f5ec5106d2a6edec4326301e327d3966c297e4d8","tid":1902813,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:57:28.000Z","msg":"pish 6"},{"pid":"e5e6c11eaa775966dc32f9e15323a8046776af3d","tid":1902813,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:46:02.000Z","msg":"pish 7"},{"pid":"0c9d4ccdcaa6cfe2d5defa672f471cdc0d551200","tid":1902813,"uid":251